------------------------------------------------
     how to compile
------------------------------------------------

1. open cs488 directory
2. premake4 gmake
3. make
4  copy the libIrrKlang.so file to your desktop
5. open cd488/A5 folder
6. premake4 gmake
7. make

-----------------------------------------------
     how to run
-----------------------------------------------

1. compile
2. at cs488/A5 directory ./A3 puppet



objectives:
 1.   Articulate(puppets' joints can work)
 2.   Animate(waling puppet)
 3.   Sky box 
 4.   Content "free" building implement correctly
 5.   Texture mapping implemented
 6.   Transparency works correctly(gradually appear/vanish)
 7.   Particle systems
 8.   Shadows
 9.   Collision system implemented(at least not through wall) 
 10.  Modeling the city
